[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0922","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0922.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1076","title":"Apple MacOS 9 空闲会话密码保护安全绕过漏洞","description":"MacOS 9 的空闲锁定功能存在安全绕过漏洞。本地攻击者可通过选择\"注销\"选项，在应用程序弹出确认对话框时选择\"取消\"，从而绕过空闲会话的密码保护机制重新进入原本已锁定的会话。该漏洞影响 MacOS 9 系统，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危，需要本地访问权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1076"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-26T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:40.277","remediation":"建议升级到后续受支持版本（Mac OS X 10.0 及以上），因为 Apple 已停止对 Mac OS 9 的支持且不再发布安全补丁。如无法升级，可在系统控制面板中关闭「空闲后需要密码」选项的「退出登录」→「取消」快捷键功能，或通过第三方屏幕锁定软件（如 ASIP Screen Lock）替代系统自带锁定机制，同时加强物理访问控制以防止本地攻击。除管理员外其他用户应设置为普通权限，限制其能够关闭系统进程的能力。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94096348604173&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/745","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1076.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1076","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1076.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1076.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1076.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-54c2-phxc-2hgx/GHSA-54c2-phxc-2hgx.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/745/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1076.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0922.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0921","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0921.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1074","title":"Webmin 密码暴力破解漏洞","description":"Webmin 0.5 之前版本存在认证机制缺陷，对有效用户名的登录密码尝试次数未作限制，远程攻击者可利用该漏洞对目标系统实施暴力枚举攻击，通过不断尝试常用或弱口令来猜测系统管理员密码，从而获取 Webmin 管理面板的访问权限并最终控制服务器。该漏洞影响 Webmin 0.5 及更早版本，属于高风险缺陷，攻击门槛较低，且无需提前获取任何认证凭据。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1074"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:40.017","remediation":"立即升级 Webmin 至 0.5 或更高版本，该版本已限制同一用户名的密码尝试次数。如无法升级，可在 Webmin 前端配置额外认证模块（如 fail2ban）限制登录频率，并在防火墙层面将 Webmin 管理端口（默认 10000）仅对可信 IP 开放，同时启用强密码策略作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/9138","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/98","http://www.webmin.com/webmin/changes.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1074.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1074","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1074.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1074.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1074.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gwfg-h74f-g6gq/GHSA-gwfg-h74f-g6gq.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/robinzixuan/attackmap/blob/3e50ba1e011308b7d6ea18a627132f0a357f36c0/Asia/bruteresult.txt","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000988.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--39926f99-82f5-4fec-ad30-6de2b1dd04dc.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0921.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0921.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0918","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0918.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0625","title":"UNIX rpc.rquotad 远程权限提升漏洞","description":"rpc.rquotad（远程磁盘配额守护进程）是基于 RPC 协议的过时服务，默认通过端口映射器注册，允许任意远程用户无需认证即可查询目标系统的用户磁盘配额信息。攻击者可通过 RPC 扫描探测该服务，从而获取系统用户名列表及配额使用情况，为后续密码爆破或权限提升攻击收集侦察信息。该协议缺乏安全认证与加密机制，属于不安全配置问题而非软件缺陷，应当禁用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0625"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:44.947","remediation":"建议立即禁用 rpc.rquotad 服务：在 Linux 中执行 `systemctl stop rpc-rquotad && systemctl disable rpc-rquotad`（或 `killall rpc.rquotad`）；在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释掉 rquotad 行并重启 inetd。同时配置 iptables 防火墙规则限制对 RPC 端口 111 和 2049 的外部访问，仅允许受信 IP 段。如在共享存储场景中必需，替换为 NFSv4 内建配额管理，不再依赖独立 rquotad 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0625","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0625.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0625","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0625.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0625.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0625.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r8qg-5ffw-4wgf/GHSA-r8qg-5ffw-4wgf.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/R/rpc_rquotad.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83127/info.html","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/1b69cf2313f68e29acceed58f52f6109cd37bb04/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0625.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0918.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0917","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0917.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1065","title":"Palm HotSync Manager 3.0.4 远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Palm Pilot HotSync Manager 3.0.4 在 Windows 98 系统中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。当 HotSync Manager 运行于网络模式时，远程攻击者可向目标系统的 14238 端口发送超长字符串，触发缓冲区溢出，导致拒绝服务，甚至可能执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Palm Pilot HotSync Manager 3.0.4 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1065"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:38.017","remediation":"立即升级 HotSync Manager 至 3.0.5 或更高版本（3Com 已承诺在新版中修复该漏洞）。在设置中将同步模式从「网络」切换为「本地串口/USB」，避免暴露 TCP 14238 端口。如必须使用网络模式，在防火墙层面添加规则阻止外部对 TCP 14238 的入站访问。由于 Palm OS 平台已停止维护，建议尽快将数据迁移至仍在支持中的现代设备。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94175465525422&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1065.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1065","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1065.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1065.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1065.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1065.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88443/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000854.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/e7bd3e92452a8dc8da42d94ae3ba208936d5a5b9/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0917.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0916","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0916.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0624","title":"Sun Microsystems RPC rstatd 服务权限提升漏洞","description":"rstatd（远程统计服务）是基于 RPC 协议运行的系统服务，默认监听在端口 111/TCP 或 111/UDP，向未经身份认证的远程攻击者提供系统性能统计数据（包括 CPU 负载、磁盘 I/O、内存使用等敏感信息）。该服务本身不提供任何访问控制机制，攻击者无需任何凭证即可通过 rpcinfo 或 rstat 协议查询目标系统，导致系统运行状态信息泄露。泄露的信息可被用于识别系统负载模式、辅助后续精准攻击。此外，常见 rstatd 实现（如 SunOS、Linux 等）历史上存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可利用特制 RPC 请求触发拒绝服务甚至远程代码执行。该漏洞影响所有运行 rstatd 服务的 UNIX/Linux 系统，属于高危暴露风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0624"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:44.800","remediation":"禁用 rstat/rstatd 服务，执行 `chkconfig rstatd off`（SysV）或 `systemctl disable rstatd && systemctl stop rstatd`（systemd），并在防火墙中封禁端口 111 (TCP/UDP，portmapper) 和 rstatd 使用的随机 UDP 端口范围，阻止外部 RPC 查询。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0624","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0624.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0624.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0624","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0624.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0624.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0624.md","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/2011/secpod_rpc_rstatd_udp.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0624.json","https://github.com/LubyRuffy/plugins/blob/f873b19f27c95eaf2993ca4acde5cb7965d2ee3f/2011/secpod_rpc_rstatd_tcp.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83127/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0916.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0915","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0915.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0623","title":"X.Org X Window System 服务配置不当","description":"CVE-1999-0623 已被 NVD 官方拒绝使用，原因为该候选编号描述的是一个系统配置检查项（X Window 服务正在运行），而非直接构成安全漏洞的缺陷。此类配置检测更适合归入通用配置枚举（CCE）体系管理，不应作为漏洞编号使用。该条目无 CVSS 评分，无有效影响范围与攻击条件说明。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0623"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.640","remediation":"若无需图形界面或远程 X11 功能，建议关闭 X Window 服务（如 Linux 下执行 `systemctl stop gdm` 并禁用开机启动）。如需使用 X11 转发，应限制仅监听 127.0.0.1，并通过 SSH 隧道（`ssh -X`）安全转发，避免将 TCP 端口 6000 暴露到外部网络。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0623.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0623","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0623.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0623.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/1b69cf2313f68e29acceed58f52f6109cd37bb04/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0623.json","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl","https://github.com/cmjayasinghe/Threat-Intelligence-Dashboard/blob/ccfec8014cc85c9e776b8f657bdb7879139ab5ed/data/cves.csv","https://github.com/Software-Engineering-2026-Class/kelompok4-cyber-kg-agentic/blob/0fc3a7d1e2416617ef834c956997e1f0f283424b/parser_agent/output/cve.ttl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0915.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0914","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0914.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0622","title":"通用 DNS 服务配置检测（非安全漏洞）","description":"CVE-1999-0622 已被正式驳回（REJECT），原候选编号描述为\"DNS 相关服务组件正在运行\"。该条目仅涉及系统配置层面的 DNS 服务开放状态，属于安全配置审计范畴而非可直接利用的安全漏洞，不存在攻击路径与利用条件。此类配置信息更适合在通用配置枚举（CCE）中覆盖，不适用作 CVE 漏洞编号。因此该 CVE 不具有实际漏洞意义，不记录 CVSS 评分。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0622"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.607","remediation":"配置 DNS 服务时应限制区域传输仅允许授权的辅助 DNS 服务器，关闭递归查询或将其限制为仅内网客户端，防止 DNS 反射放大攻击。同时部署 DNSSEC 保障数据完整性，禁止版本信息泄露，并定期审计 DNS 日志。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0622.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0622","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0622.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0622.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/RiskBasedPrioritization/RiskBasedPrioritizationAnalysis/blob/3d5cc1819ecb8cbc3aeb75d9a8260318544faf56/data_in/acme/acme_cves.csv","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/1b69cf2313f68e29acceed58f52f6109cd37bb04/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0622.json","https://github.com/aboutcode-org/aboutcode-mirror-euvd/blob/1b758e4b71978ff973a6df1bc69fc70b932735fb/advisories/2000/02/EUVD-1999-0605.json","https://github.com/Software-Engineering-2026-Class/kelompok4-cyber-kg-agentic/blob/0fc3a7d1e2416617ef834c956997e1f0f283424b/parser_agent/output/cve.ttl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0914.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0913","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0913.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1060","title":"Tetrix TetriNet 守护进程缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Tetrix TetriNet 后台守护进程 1.13.16 版本存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过连接该服务监听的 31457 端口，并提供一个超长的 DNS 主机名触发缓冲区溢出，导致目标服务进程崩溃造成拒绝服务，在特定条件下可能执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 TetriNet 1.13.16 及可能更早的版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1060"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-02-17T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:37.310","remediation":"升级 tetrinetx 到已应用补丁的版本（>1.13.16），或将 UHOSTLEN 从 30 改为 256，将 main.c 中栈缓冲区从 121 改为 UHOSTLEN，并将 net.c 中的 strcpy 替换为 strncpy。临时缓解措施：在防火墙上限制 TCP 31457 端口的访问来源。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91937090211855&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/340","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1060.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1060.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1060","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1060.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1060.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1060.md","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1060.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--6a35e01f-9c82-4365-a727-7af8d726e1c6.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000529.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0913.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0913.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0912","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0912.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0621","title":"Various vendors NETBIOS 组件服务配置不当","description":"该候选编号已被拒绝。原条目仅描述 NETBIOS 相关组件服务处于运行状态，属于安全配置范畴而非可直接引入安全漏洞的缺陷。此类配置问题更适合由通用配置枚举（CCE）覆盖管理，因此该 CVE 编号作废，建议参考 CCE 标准进行安全配置检查。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0621"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.540","remediation":"禁用 NetBIOS over TCP/IP：在网络连接属性中取消选中\"Microsoft 网络的文件和打印机共享\"的绑定，或在高级 TCP/IP 设置中禁用 NetBIOS。在防火墙层面，阻止外部访问 UDP 137-138 和 TCP 139、445 端口。如业务不需要，直接停止 Server 服务并禁用 SMBv1。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0621.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0621","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0621.json","https://github.com/Azure/Azure-Sentinel/blob/c359f282ec6bc3eb6912ee4649970789e923d257/Sample%20Data/Custom/beSECURE_ScanResults_CL.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/netbios_name_get.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0621.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/gitpan/QualysGuard-Request/blob/d9b44790f3fe9c775d3c27df315f23d890890583/t/02-ticket_list.t","https://github.com/opexxx/Metasploit-Unleashed-ebook/blob/c8c7947d4d4a18382b92c12c7ece8573da39c1de/05_vulnerability_scanning/06_working_with_nessus/working_with_nessus.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0621.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0912.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0911","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0911.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1058","title":"Vermillion FTP Daemon 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Vermillion FTP Daemon VFTPD 1.23 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 FTP 服务器发送多个特制的超长 CWD 命令触发该漏洞，导致服务进程崩溃引发拒绝服务，在特定条件下甚至可能执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 VFTPD 1.23 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，建议升级或限制访问以降低风险。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1058"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-22T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:37.050","remediation":"立即停止使用已停止维护的 Vermillion FTP Daemon VFTPD 1.23，迁移至现代活跃维护的 FTP 服务器（如 vsftpd 或 ProFTPD），或在条件允许时改用 SFTP/FTPS 替代 FTP 协议。如暂时无法迁移，应在网络边界防火墙限制对 FTP 端口（默认 21）的访问来源 IP，并使用 IPS/IDS 规则检测并阻断超长 CWD 命令（正常 CWD 路径长度通常不超过 256 字符）以缓解缓冲区溢出风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94329968617085&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=94337185023159&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/818","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3543","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1058.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1058","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1058.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1058.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1058.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7cj6-wm7r-4g46/GHSA-7cj6-wm7r-4g46.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/V/vftpd_overflow.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/818/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1058.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0911.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0910","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0910.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0620","title":"NIS 相关服务运行配置问题","description":"该漏洞编号已被 NVD 驳回，原描述为目标系统上运行了 NIS（Network Information System）组件服务。NIS 协议在设计上缺乏加密和认证机制，通过网络在局域网内传输用户账户数据（包括密码哈希）时，处于同一网段的攻击者可进行网络嗅探，捕获 NIS 映射数据后实施离线破解，进而获取系统访问权限。该问题属于安全配置核查范畴，并非传统代码层面的安全漏洞，广泛影响启用 NIS 服务的 Unix/Linux 系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0620"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.480","remediation":"如业务无需 NIS 服务，应停止 ypserv/ypbind 服务并设置开机不自启：systemctl disable --now ypserv ypbind。如确需使用 NIS，应在 /var/yp/securenets 中限定仅允许受信任子网访问，并避免与互联网直连。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0620.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0620","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0620.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0620.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/1b69cf2313f68e29acceed58f52f6109cd37bb04/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-06xx/CVE-1999-0620.json","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl","https://github.com/cmjayasinghe/Threat-Intelligence-Dashboard/blob/ccfec8014cc85c9e776b8f657bdb7879139ab5ed/data/cves.csv","https://github.com/Software-Engineering-2026-Class/kelompok4-cyber-kg-agentic/blob/0fc3a7d1e2416617ef834c956997e1f0f283424b/parser_agent/output/cve.ttl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0910.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0909","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0909.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0835","title":"ISC BIND named 畸形 SIG 记录拒绝服务漏洞","description":"ISC BIND 的域名解析服务 named 在处理畸形的 SIG 资源记录时存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需任何认证即可向目标 DNS 服务器发送特制的 SIG 记录查询数据包，触发 named 进程崩溃（如断言失败或段错误），导致正常的域名解析服务中断。该漏洞影响 ISC BIND 8.2.2p1 及之前版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。建议用户升级至 BIND 8.2.2p2 或更高版本修复此问题。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0835"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:09.437","remediation":"升级 ISC BIND 至 8.2.2-p2 或更高版本（如 9.x 系列），该版本修复了 named 处理畸形 SIG 记录时的空指针解引用问题。如无法立即升级，可在边界防火墙上限制对 DNS 服务器的外部递归查询，并启用 ACL 仅允许受信来源访问。建议部署多台冗余 DNS 服务器分摊风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/788"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0909.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0908","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0908.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0834","title":"RSA Security RSAREF 2.0 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"RSA Security RSAREF 2.0 库中的加密与解密函数存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可向受影响的应用程序传递特制的输入数据，触发缓冲区溢出，导致拒绝服务或任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 RSAREF 2.0 版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。建议用户升级至修复版本或禁用受影响的库函数调用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0834"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:09.317","remediation":"RSAREF 2.0 已停止维护，建议立即停止使用该库，迁移至 OpenSSL 3.x 或 libsodium 等现代密码学库。在代码中对所有加解密函数传入的参数进行长度校验，限制输入缓冲区大小不超过预期值，避免直接拼接用户可控数据作为函数参数。如无法立即替换库，应对调用 RSAREF 的代码层增加边界检查与异常处理作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/843","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19655"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0908.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0907","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0907.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0619","title":"通用 Telnet 服务配置不当问题","description":"该候选编号已被拒绝，原描述为\"Telnet 服务正在运行\"。Telnet 协议以明文传输所有数据（包括用户名和密码），未提供任何加密或认证机制，远程攻击者可通过网络嗅探拦截并窃取敏感凭据。此条目属于安全配置问题（不应启用不安全的 Telnet 服务）而非软件漏洞，因此被移入通用配置枚举（CCE）进行管理，建议使用 SSH 等安全替代方案。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0619"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:59.450","remediation":"关闭 Telnet 服务（端口 23），改用 SSH（端口 22）进行远程管理。如因兼容性无法禁用，应在防火墙限制 Telnet 的源 IP 访问范围，仅允许受信任的管理网段连接，并启用加密通道（如 stunnel）封装 Telnet 流量。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0619.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0619","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0619.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0619.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/harshsingh4469/endpoint-security-analyzer/blob/39935d29fd093a995963ab16d1953b9224b57717/scanner.py","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000455.txt","https://github.com/SwethaV0611/Network_vuln/blob/fce59788552720e2cf78ee52ee7c584a9475da61/scanner/vulnerability.py","https://github.com/athiasjerome/XORCISM/blob/327e2a3be196660f82c89ae9d7c4e7abe4785b0d/SOURCES/XProviderQualys/QualysSampleResults.xml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0907.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0906","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0906.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0832","title":"Linux NFS 服务器缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Linux NFS 服务器中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标 NFS 服务发送特制的超长路径名请求触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出并执行任意代码。该漏洞影响早期 Linux 内核版本中运行的 NFS 服务，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，危害严重。建议用户升级至修复版本或限制 NFS 服务的网络访问权限。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0832"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-09T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:09.053","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至 2.2.13 及以上版本，该版本修复了 NFS 服务处理长路径名时的缓冲区溢出问题。如无法升级内核，可在不需要 NFS 服务的系统上禁用 NFS 服务（如 `chkconfig nfs off`），或通过防火墙限制对 NFS 端口（2049/TCP/UDP）的访问。同时建议启用 ASLR 等内核防护机制作为纵深防御。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.debian.org/security/1999/19991111","http://www.novell.com/linux/security/advisories/suse_security_announce_29.html","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh42-errata-general.html#NFS","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/782","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=Pine.LNX.4.20.9911091058140.12964-100000%40mail.zigzag.pl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0906.toml"}]